Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.96,0:03:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一方面那樣滿腹狐疑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.19,0:03:34.94,Note,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,0)\fs34\bord0\c&H9B99A9&\frx6\fry2\move(873,222,903,254,402,2737)}劇\N目
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.19,0:03:34.94,Note,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,0)\fs34\bord0\c&H9B99A9&\frx6\fry2\move(878,318,912,358,26,2737)}奧\N賽\N羅
