Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.49,0:03:35.20,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\be10\blur5\fs42} ※此話中出現的劇本台詞均出自於《奧賽羅》第三幕第三場
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.46,0:03:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一方面又是那樣痴心疼愛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.25,0:03:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\blur5}這才是活活的受罪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.26,0:03:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊 表演的日子馬上就要到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.10,0:03:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好緊張啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.42,0:03:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}桃子你練習了那麼多肯定很輕鬆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.18,0:03:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是 正式表演會如何誰也不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.62,0:03:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}總之 只要能快快樂樂地表演就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.12,0:03:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真不愧是你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.62,0:03:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}吶 七海你台詞都背好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.48,0:03:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}七海？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.32,0:04:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 難說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.16,0:04:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們都指望著你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.70,0:04:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大家一起加油 讓我們組全員都合格吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.24,0:04:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.46,0:04:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我必須更努力才行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.96,0:04:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.54,0:04:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}買東西回來晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.20,0:04:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}今天吃蛋包飯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.94,0:04:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是的 做起來比較省事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.68,0:04:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}覺得做蛋包飯比較省事的七海
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.76,0:04:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}女性魅力簡直像喜馬拉雅山一樣高
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.02,0:04:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}太誇張啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.82,0:04:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我去叫學弟和仁過來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.26,0:04:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊 今天我值日 我去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.12,0:04:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}太過完美？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.32,0:04:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}椎名同學 吃晚餐…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.04,0:04:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}發售日是…指雜誌的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.44,0:04:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}跟我的表演是同一天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.28,0:04:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就快到了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.36,0:05:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}椎名同學 我幫你把扣子縫上去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.32,0:05:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}另外記得把要洗的衣服拿出來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.68,0:05:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}您要留心嫉妒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.90,0:05:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嫉妒是一個綠眼的妖魔…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.84,0:05:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}誰做了它的犧牲 就要受它的玩弄
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.66,0:05:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}七海太緊繃了...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.74,0:05:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在煩惱桃花期遲遲不來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.75,0:05:46.89,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\be10\blur5}※ 日本有個傳說 每人一生會有三次受歡迎的時期。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.72,0:05:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.82,0:05:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那是都市傳說哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.08,0:05:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}都說不是…咦 是真的嗎？！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.26,0:05:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}虧我還一直相信著
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.16,0:05:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不過你的情況 就是發現沒發現的問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.56,0:05:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那個 仁學長 有時間嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.38,0:06:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}於是 想說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.92,0:06:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是關於青山的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.50,0:06:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}被告白了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.50,0:06:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}戲弄我就那麼好玩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.48,0:06:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.44,0:06:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}擔心青山同學嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.20,0:06:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}與其說是擔心…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.21,0:06:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}青山確實精明能幹 大部份的事情都能做得比一般人好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.70,0:06:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是所有事一個人全包了也太亂來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.08,0:06:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}畢竟大家住在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.12,0:06:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}互相幫助也沒什麼不可以的吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.68,0:06:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}跟我對青山同學的印象大不一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.90,0:06:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}算了 但是我想青山同學她也有很多自己的想法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.36,0:06:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}找到了目標 不顧父母的反對
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.27,0:06:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}走出家門之後一直都是靠自己一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.94,0:06:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我想她一定覺得無論什麼事都必須自己解決吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.46,0:06:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還有真白的事也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.52,0:06:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}咦？椎名？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.15,0:06:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}像這種事唯有她本人認可才行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.14,0:06:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}意思是讓我別管她嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.95,0:06:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是我的話會這樣做
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.24,0:07:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}空太你會如何抉擇我就不知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.00,0:07:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}思考是一件好事哦 學弟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.72,0:07:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}別用那種叫法啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.34,0:07:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.60,0:07:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大阪？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.77,0:07:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}仁學長 這是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.78,0:07:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}如你所見
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.44,0:07:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不會去水明大學 而是去大阪的藝術大學
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.76,0:07:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那美咲學姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.74,0:07:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們又不是在交往
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.08,0:07:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.28,0:07:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}別跟美咲說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.08,0:07:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我會自己對她說的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.88,0:07:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你別一副那麼深沉的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.34,0:07:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一如既往 你什麼都不知道 很簡單的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.22,0:07:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}今後叫我怎麼面對美咲學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.44,0:07:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}仁學長到底想怎麼樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.66,0:07:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼面對我是指什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.20,0:07:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你什麼時候開始在那裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.12,0:07:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}才剛到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.60,0:07:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}仁怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.92,0:08:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不 啊 那個…是跟他談了關於企劃書的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.04,0:08:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}完全沒有提到關於美咲學姐的話題啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.14,0:08:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}咦 我？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.98,0:08:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯... 這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.88,0:08:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}美...美咲學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.94,0:08:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}吶 學弟…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.54,0:08:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼做…才能讓仁留意到我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.92,0:08:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}學姐想和仁學長成為什麼關係
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.62,0:08:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}什麼關係…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.52,0:08:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}像戀人般 親吻之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.56,0:08:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}想牽著手一起散步 想被他緊緊抱住
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.96,0:08:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是我不知道該怎麼做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.70,0:08:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大家都是怎麼成為戀人的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.16,0:08:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}學弟…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.77,0:08:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}幫幫我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.22,0:09:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}學姐很可愛的所以沒關係的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.48,0:09:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為了打起精神要來打場遊戲嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.02,0:09:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}竟敢挑戰我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.24,0:09:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}成長了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.78,0:09:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}學弟 暑假剩下的時間裡 我們盡情地去玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.60,0:09:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.66,0:09:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對我和仁來說這是最後的暑假了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.62,0:09:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}青山小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.52,0:09:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你沒事吧 別太勉強了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.24,0:09:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對不起 我不小心絆了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.80,0:09:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我真是笨拙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.52,0:10:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.64,0:10:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}10
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.58,0:10:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}9
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.57,0:10:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}8
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.26,0:10:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}7…啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.96,0:10:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我說你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.44,0:10:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}空太
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.22,0:10:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}痛痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.52,0:10:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.76,0:10:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}七海很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.00,0:10:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}青山
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.24,0:10:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼了怎麼了 真白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.54,0:10:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}七海怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.08,0:10:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}青山同學
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.21,0:10:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\blur5}七海
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.52,0:10:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}喂 青山 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.56,0:10:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}青山 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.18,0:10:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我要去 今天一定要去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.68,0:10:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}拜託了 讓我去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.40,0:10:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}偏偏是在這種時候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.42,0:10:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雖然我早就覺得她這樣勉強自己遲早會出問題
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.44,0:11:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}聲優培訓所的表演是今天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.33,0:11:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我想她是為了不讓我們注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.29,0:11:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}才想早點出門的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.74,0:11:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雖然本人是想去的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.46,0:11:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不可能讓她去的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.14,0:11:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雖然很可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.02,0:11:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.46,0:11:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}換做我的話我會去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.94,0:11:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是我的話 我會去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.10,0:11:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是 椎名…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.30,0:11:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}既然七海想去的話 就讓她去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.14,0:11:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}讓她去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.59,0:11:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.40,0:11:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}七海 很努力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.75,0:11:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}每天練習到很晚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.55,0:11:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這些我當然知道 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.56,0:11:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.10,0:11:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}椎名
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.10,0:11:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}慢慢走就好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.40,0:12:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}吵死了 從剛才起你們在鬧什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.54,0:12:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}青山
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.76,0:12:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.66,0:12:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.94,0:12:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}讓我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.68,0:12:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你發這麼高的燒還想出門？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.86,0:12:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}去休息
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.08,0:12:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.26,0:12:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我才不管你願不願意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.55,0:12:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}回到房裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.46,0:12:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}計程車來了 快點！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.30,0:12:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}公主大人我們就接走了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.94,0:12:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\blur5}等等 給我站住…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.46,0:12:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}空太 接下來就交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.54,0:12:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\blur5}喂 你們幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.28,0:12:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.86,0:12:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}七海 坐好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.84,0:12:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}學弟也快點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.80,0:12:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.57,0:12:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\blur5}上吧 上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.70,0:12:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}走吧 椎名
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.86,0:12:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好的 那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.09,0:12:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}前進吧 計程車 Go Go！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.48,0:12:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\blur5}三鷹 別趁亂摸我胸部啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.22,0:12:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因為那裡有胸部嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.92,0:12:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}別說的像登山一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.78,0:12:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}青山 你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.40,0:12:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.78,0:13:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝謝 接下來我一個人就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.56,0:13:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}結束的時候我們也會在這裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.74,0:13:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.18,0:13:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}青山小姐 找你很久了 趕快進來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.10,0:13:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.72,0:13:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}去咖啡店吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.64,0:13:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就待在這
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.89,0:13:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還有很長時間哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.02,0:13:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.17,0:13:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是因為我的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.44,0:13:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.90,0:13:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}七海 太累了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.40,0:13:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.26,0:13:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不道歉的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.86,0:13:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.26,0:13:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她肯定會生氣的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.58,0:13:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.28,0:14:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雨下的真突然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.12,0:14:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}買把傘吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.10,0:14:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊 不好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.00,0:14:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}「那到時候一起去買吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.71,0:14:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}抱歉 慌慌張張的完全忘記是今天了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.73,0:14:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.66,0:14:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼會沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.43,0:14:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒必要執著於發售日
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.44,0:14:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}看 這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.88,0:14:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不看一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.70,0:14:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}內容我都知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.70,0:14:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}即使如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.82,0:14:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}難道你不太高興嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.48,0:14:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.62,0:14:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.95,0:14:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哇 果然下雨了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.32,0:14:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}跑步去車站
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.18,0:14:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}咦 不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.94,0:14:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}青山
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.74,0:15:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}等一下 七海
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.08,0:15:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你知道因為你的關係給大家添了多少麻煩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.96,0:15:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.90,0:15:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}與其發展成這樣 你還不如就待在家裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.38,0:15:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.42,0:15:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.88,0:15:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}給你們添了這麼多麻煩 真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.36,0:15:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.04,0:15:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}什麼都沒做成
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.22,0:15:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}難得你們願意帶我來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.28,0:15:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明明為了今天一直在準備
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.21,0:15:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}結果全都白費了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.80,0:15:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我太差勁了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.49,0:15:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真的太糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.46,0:15:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}已經沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.88,0:15:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}才不會沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.66,0:15:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你也說過
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.61,0:16:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}說我太逞強 太亂來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.82,0:16:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}自己承擔著這麼多工作 還以為能做的更好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.77,0:16:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}結果就一個勁地逞強 我真是個笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.76,0:16:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒事的 青山
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.50,0:16:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不用在乎我說的那些話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.22,0:16:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不要這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.00,0:16:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}說我是個傻女人 嘲笑我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.38,0:16:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不然的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.28,0:16:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不然的話 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.76,0:16:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}別那樣說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.24,0:16:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}如果青山是笨蛋的話 世界上的人豈不是都是笨蛋了嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.18,0:16:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}什麼啊 別開玩笑了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.54,0:16:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}神田同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.05,0:16:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}青山已經很努力了 這點我們都很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.14,0:16:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼 為什麼要那麼說…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.72,0:16:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}聽到你這樣說的話 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.42,0:16:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.66,0:16:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一直很希望能有人這樣對我說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.22,0:17:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}七海一直勉強著自己呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.15,0:17:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因為她是那種對別人或自己都很嚴格的類型
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.36,0:17:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嘛 或許她只是想保持那樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.78,0:17:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我總算明白仁所說的「印象不同」的意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.90,0:17:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}青山一直在跟什麼奮戰著
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.06,0:17:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}例如父母的反對 以及與自身等等
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.60,0:17:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也許是一直沒有可以依靠的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.36,0:17:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怕自己只要懈怠了一次 就會一錯再錯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.06,0:17:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只能逞強著 把自己逼入了絕境
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.90,0:17:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}能有人明白這一點 她也算是有所回報了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.24,0:17:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小真白還陪在青山身邊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.90,0:17:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 好像很放心不下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.38,0:18:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.68,0:18:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.80,0:18:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.25,0:18:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}人參雞湯 我想這種時候還是來點特別的火鍋比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.82,0:18:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}特別？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.04,0:18:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因為七海把脆弱的一面展露出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.96,0:18:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}脆弱的一面…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.28,0:18:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}話說人參雞湯根本不是火鍋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.42,0:18:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}太在意細節的話 會錯過桃花期的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.76,0:18:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}虎次郎 我該怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.24,0:18:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\3c&H007FFF&}我怎麼會知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.23,0:18:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是 昨天也太難為情了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.21,0:18:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}被他看到我哭得那麼慘
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.37,0:18:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雖說發燒了 但我一直都靠在他身上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.70,0:18:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\3c&H007FFF&}趁亂就黏著不放吶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.70,0:18:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我又不是故意的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.02,0:18:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\3c&H007FFF&}不要磨嘰磨嘰的 趕快去推倒他吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.48,0:18:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}等…虎次郎！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.21,0:18:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那就是虎次郎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.58,0:19:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}等...敲個門啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.00,0:19:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}敲了 而且門是開著的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.98,0:19:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}討厭…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.19,0:19:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真沒想到這個抱枕 原來還有說話功能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.83,0:19:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}別告訴別人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.81,0:19:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.84,0:19:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真是糟透了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.40,0:19:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}給
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.12,0:19:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這個樣子好像不行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.93,0:19:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.62,0:19:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不快點吃就冷掉了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.60,0:19:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.10,0:19:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要謝的話就謝謝仁學長吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.28,0:19:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}話說…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.58,0:19:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 好像整晚都握著我的手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.19,0:19:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}似乎是感覺到了責任
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.57,0:19:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.95,0:20:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}而且 最了解青山的人是椎名
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.32,0:20:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要不是椎名的話 我就阻止你去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.31,0:20:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是 她說「換做是我的話 我會去」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.08,0:20:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}「請帶她去吧」 向大家低下了頭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.88,0:20:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你努力的樣子她一直都看在眼裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.68,0:20:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.48,0:20:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}如果沒去的話 我肯定會後悔的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.68,0:20:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.44,0:20:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}看著椎名 我就會覺得自己做得還遠遠不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.89,0:20:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.16,0:20:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}每天都畫漫畫到很晚 一遍又一遍地改過重畫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.46,0:20:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我原以為有才能的人是不會努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.04,0:20:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要怎麼做 才能追上有才能的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.30,0:20:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}追上…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.30,0:20:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}別盯著看！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.16,0:20:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}椎名同學的睡臉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.32,0:20:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}看房間也不行！也不准看我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.45,0:20:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那我該看哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.74,0:20:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還有不准太接近我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.48,0:20:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}總覺得有點受傷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.78,0:21:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因為 我都還沒洗澡…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.54,0:21:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.90,0:21:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我是說人參雞湯很好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.64,0:21:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}早安 椎名同學
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.41,0:21:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}七海 已經沒事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.22,0:21:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 多虧了你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.84,0:21:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}神田同學 關於照顧真白的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.84,0:21:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}抱歉 說實話我沒有辦法繼續照顧她了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.86,0:21:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雖然不是照顧不了她 但以我現在的處境…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.14,0:21:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我明白了 謝謝你 願意依靠我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.74,0:21:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}該道謝的是我 抱歉 椎名同學
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.10,0:21:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真白
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.64,0:21:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}希望七海能叫我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.52,0:21:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我知道了 真白
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.48,0:21:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.06,0:21:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}等等 椎…真白
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.64,0:21:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}神田同學 想想辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.22,0:21:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}負責照顧她的人是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.95,0:21:59.75,Note,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\bord0\c&H575757&\move(150,50,100,10,20,7779)}『真白的保姆』由青山七海換回神田空太。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.95,0:21:59.75,Note,,0,0,0,,{\c&H575757&\shad0\bord0\move(165,483,100,509,20,7779)}神田同學，給你添了不少麻煩對不起。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.95,0:21:59.75,Note,,0,0,0,,{\c&H575757&\shad0\bord0\move(168,533,100,559,20,7779)}有句話忘了說就寫在這裡吧。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.95,0:21:59.75,Note,,0,0,0,,{\c&H575757&&\shad0\bord0\move(170,586,100,612,20,7779)}要是敢對真白做什麼奇怪的事情的話 我絕對饒不了你！
Dialogue: 1,0:21:52.44,0:21:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}事已至此 為時已晚了
Dialogue: 1,0:21:53.76,0:21:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}打也打不醒的
Dialogue: 1,0:21:55.92,0:21:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}快起來 真白 真白！
Comment: 0,0:21:59.75,0:21:59.80,ED2-JP,,0,0,0,,ED
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.00,0:22:05.61,ED2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}過ぎるだけの  時間じゃ悔しい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.00,0:22:05.61,ED2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}一味流逝的時光 徒增懊悔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.97,0:22:08.44,ED2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}刻まなくちゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.97,0:22:08.19,ED2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}唯有銘記於心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.44,0:22:14.45,ED2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}「此処にいる」と心が叫ぶ瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.47,0:22:14.58,ED2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}「我就在這裡」 內心如此吶喊的瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.60,0:22:16.99,ED2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}I'm dreaming
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.58,0:22:16.99,ED2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}I'm dreaming
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.02,0:22:23.63,ED2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}迷いながら  涙を飲み込んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.02,0:22:23.63,ED2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}不斷迷茫著 逞強噙住眼角淚水
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.03,0:22:30.00,ED2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}不器用だね　夢も遠回り
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.03,0:22:29.76,ED2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}真是笨拙呢 連夢想都不斷繞道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.00,0:22:35.76,ED2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}大空を見上げ　何も見えず
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.03,0:22:35.94,ED2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}仰望這片廣闊的天空 卻無法確認一物
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.94,0:22:44.06,ED2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}胸が痛むわけ考えていた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.96,0:22:44.19,ED2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}也曾思考過內心會如此疼痛的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.21,0:22:45.59,ED2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}DAYS  of  DASH
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.19,0:22:45.59,ED2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}DAYS of DASH
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.59,0:22:48.53,ED2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}風を走り抜けて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.59,0:22:48.44,ED2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}飛奔而出 風聲過耳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.53,0:22:54.85,ED2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}君と僕の中で　何が始まったのだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.55,0:22:54.85,ED2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}在你與我的內心中 究竟有什麼開始了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.85,0:22:56.95,ED2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}わからないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.85,0:22:57.01,ED2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}雖然沒有答案
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.01,0:23:04.54,ED2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}キラキラ光る太陽が照らす場所をずっと進もう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.02,0:23:04.63,ED2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}但是就朝著炫目陽光照耀的地方一直前進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.63,0:23:10.42,ED2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}永遠など　知らないけれど
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.65,0:23:10.42,ED2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}雖然無法知道 何謂永恆
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.14,0:23:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}空太 幫我吹吹頭髮
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.92,0:23:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.50,0:23:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}恭喜你出道
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.22,0:23:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.68,0:23:39.93,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\alpha&H00&\shad0\blur3\3c&H4BBBEF&\pos(680,450)}妹妹來襲
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.48,0:23:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}優子 要來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.24,0:23:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}優子 要登場囉！
